quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,"Kandi ubu buzima bw’isi nta kindi buri cyo uretse kuba ari umukino no kwinezeza, ariko mu by’ukuri, inzu yo ku munsi w’imperuka (Ijuru) ni bwo buzima nyakuri, iyaba bari babizi"
  29,65,"N’iyo bagiye mu bwato (bagahuriramo n’ingorane), basaba Allah bamwibombaritseho. Maze yabageza imusozi amahoro, bagahita bamubangikanya"
  29,66,Kugira ngo bahakane ibyo twabahaye (tubarokora) kandi banishimishe. Vuba aha bazamenya (ingaruka z’ibyo bakoze)
  29,67,"Ese ntibabona ko twagize (Maka) ahantu hatagatifu kandi hatekanye, mu gihe mu nkengero zabo abantu bashimutwa? Nonese bemera ibitari ukuri bagahakana inema za Allah"
  29,68,"Ni nde nkozi y’ibibikurusha uwahimbiye Allah ikinyoma, cyangwa awahakanye ukuri kwamugezeho? Ese mu muriro wa Jahanamu si ho cyicaro cy’abahakanyi"
  29,69,"Kandi babandi baharanira inzira yacu kubera twe (Allah), rwose tuzabayobora inzira zacu. Ndetse mu by’ukuri, Allah ari kumwe n’abakora ibyiza"
  30,1,Alif Laam Miim
  30,2,Abaromani baratsinzwe
  30,3,Mu gihugu cyo hafi (y’Abaperise) 98. Ariko nyuma yo gutsindwa kwabo na bo bazatsinda
  30,4,Mu myaka mike (iri hagati y’itatu n’icumi)! Umwanzuro ni uwa Allah mbere (yo gutsinda kw’Abaromani) na nyuma (yaho). Kandi icyo gihe abemeramana bazishima
  30,5,"Ku bw’inkunga ya Allah (azatera Abaromani bagatsinda Abaperise). Atera inkunga uwo ashaka kandi we ni Umunyembaraga zihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"